n原廠維修聽fiesta st D師兄講無咩特別有問題，如果考慮埋二手承接就真係唔好考慮ford，巴打唔考慮買15年二手? 有人食左折讓價再放出去無咁入肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bdfc1c3028e7bf682f614e8de57ccd3f13ae63","tid":139082,"uid":65443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T08:29:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢排開始睇七人車，bmw 2/ Sienta 後排 dog seat 唔鍾意，box type 又太似渣貨van, 見到 Grand c-max 21萬幾好似好抵屌⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n除左冇電趟，有冇咩理由唔考慮？而家Ford轉左代理，原廠維修 o 唔 ok?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n21萬好似係16年車，試坐過尾排比日本車好座不過收埋無日本車咁大空間，最欣賞中排可以收張凳落右邊位3座變2座，同類設計得日產serena有，千五turbo同級應該無對手，揸到劏其實幾抵玩<br />\n<br />\n原廠維修聽fiesta st D師兄講無咩特別有問題，如果考慮埋二手承接就真係唔好考慮ford，巴打唔考慮買15年二手? 有人食左折讓價再放出去無咁入肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都鍾意佢中排收凳設計，對後排上落車真係方便左好多（雖然我更鍾意Freed張凳可以摺到勁細）<br />\n<br />\n二手唔識搵，上網搵又驚俾人呃，又冇相熟車房⋯"},{"pid":"798ae12186eddb38a6bf2bf943e49052f70844e1","tid":139082,"uid":65443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T08:32:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢排開始睇七人車，bmw 2/ Sienta 後排 dog seat 唔鍾意，box type 又太似渣貨van, 見到 Grand c-max 21萬幾好似好抵屌⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n除左冇電趟，有冇咩理由唔考慮？而家Ford轉左代理，原廠維修 o 唔 ok?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大霸呢？</blockquote><br />\n大霸貴一截⋯⋯同埋大架，屋企隻乸冇信心舞得掂。如果買大車我可能會 odyssey/ stepwagon, 甚至XC90/ Sorento"},{"pid":"770fbee2d5f2a185048b1ac0d71ae35a30987218","tid":139082,"uid":65443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T08:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢排開始睇七人車，bmw 2/ Sienta 後排 dog seat 唔鍾意，box type 又太似渣貨van, 見到 Grand c-max 21萬幾好似好抵屌⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n除左冇電趟，有冇咩理由唔考慮？而家Ford轉左代理，原廠維修 o 唔 ok?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nVW部Touran 好似249k咋喎<br />\nFord冷門，會唔會難放？</blockquote><br />\nTouran 後排同寶馬2有得揮咁窄，同埋傳統車門減十分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbf4d26d5811dd5e28d7ec11ed50071f3f86a51","tid":139082,"uid":43611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"依家ford好失禮你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗清楚二手價同冇人接貨呢個問題。廠保養不過不失啦。番過幾次都冇咩問題"},{"pid":"cfaf949be2c94a52aba73ec741c5674e0d3fb661","tid":139082,"uid":3578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:05:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家ford好失禮你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗清楚二手價同冇人接貨呢個問題。廠保養不過不失啦。番過幾次都冇咩問題</blockquote><br />\n英之傑維修都ok嘅<br />\n但親戚做維修中心<br />\n話ford成日壞但冇零件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01edca6c60c08908e5088fd7ecc6b926e222ad11","tid":139082,"uid":32013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:10:29.000Z","msg":"C-Max/S-Max都係好車<br />\n啱就入手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我錯過咗&hellip;好後悔</span></span>"},{"pid":"6328269841a74ff9bad338dc644ce6e8d8ffe8fa","tid":139082,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:14:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢排開始睇七人車，bmw 2/ Sienta 後排 dog seat 唔鍾意，box type 又太似渣貨van, 見到 Grand c-max 21萬幾好似好抵屌⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n除左冇電趟，有冇咩理由唔考慮？而家Ford轉左代理，原廠維修 o 唔 ok?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大霸呢？</blockquote><br />\n大霸貴一截⋯⋯同埋大架，屋企隻乸冇信心舞得掂。如果買大車我可能會 odyssey/ stepwagon, 甚至XC90/ Sorento</blockquote